```plantuml
@startuml beston123_Tarzan

package "Tarzan Distributed Transaction System" {
    [Client] as Client
    [Server] as Server
    [Registry (Zookeeper)] as Registry
    [Message Broker (RocketMQ)] as Broker
    [Store (MySQL + Redis)] as Store

    component "tarzan-rpc (Netty)" as RPC {
        [RpcClient]
        [RpcServer]
    }

    component "tarzan-server" as ServerModule {
        [ConfigManager]
        [ScheduledServiceManager]
        [MessageResendService]
        [ServerController]
    }

    component "tarzan-store" as StoreModule {
        [RocketMQStoreService]
        [ToSendMessage]
        [MessageConsume]
    }

    component "tarzan-mq" as MQModule {
        [RocketMQMessageNotifier]
        [RocketMQTransactionChecker]
    }
}

Client --> RPC : Uses
Client --> Broker : Sends messages
Server --> RPC : Hosts
Server --> Registry : Registers
Server --> Broker : Proxies messages
Server --> Store : Persists data
ServerModule --> StoreModule : Manages transactions
ServerModule --> MQModule : Handles notifications
StoreModule --> Store : Data access
MQModule --> Broker : Message operations
Registry --> Server : Service discovery

note top of Client: Initiates transactions\nand message flow
note right of Server: Central coordinator\nwith scheduled recovery
note left of Broker: Primary message transport
note bottom of Store: Persistent storage\nwith Redis locks

@enduml
```